{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "sc-br-rp-30d-iter5",
    "name": "StableCoin-BackingRatio-RedemptionPressure-30d-iter5",
    "description": "APPROACH 3 iter5 — BACKING RATIO + REDEMPTION PRESSURE.\n\nPortfolio: $101,000 reserves / $100,000 token supply (1% over-collateral)\n  L1 cash/tbills: $85,000  L2A commpaper: $6,000  L2B defi: $4,000\n  Starting liquidity: ($12k+$11k)/$100k = 23.0% (above 20% MiCA Art.45)\n\nTHRESHOLDS (GENIUS/MiCA — unchanged from iter5):\n  BACKING_THRESHOLD  = 1.00 (100% MtM-adjusted)\n  LIQUIDITY_THRESHOLD= 0.20 (20% cash/supply — MiCA Art.45)\n\n30-DAY LIFECYCLE — MINT HALT AND RESTORE:\n  Day 1:   MINT ALLOWED — backing 101.1%, liquidity 23.0%\n  Days 2-3: Peg creeps up (0.05-0.1%) — cadence escalates\n  Days 4-6: Peg 0.1-0.3% — WATCH cadence — redemption begins\n  Days 7-10: EW signals fire — ELEVATED — redemption accelerates\n  Day 11:  \u2605 MINT HALTED — EW=4/4 fires simultaneously\n           Redemption rate: peg ~1.3% = 5.7%/day\n  Days 11-17: HALTED — liquidity drains 23% \u2192 17%\n              Backing stays 101% (rate shock mild, max 8bps)\n  Day 18:  \u2605 tbill-4wk-001 matures \u2192 +$10,000 cash\n             Liquidity: 17.0% \u2192 28.1% (above 20% threshold)\n             EW signals cleared (all 4 below threshold)\n  Day 19:  \u2605 MINT RESTORED — all 4 conditions met\n  Days 20-30: De-escalation, normal redemption tapers\n\nKEY CHANGE vs stablecoin-1:\n  Reserves $101k (not $102M), supply $100k\n  liquidityThreshold=0.20 (MiCA Art.45, not 0.35)\n  backingThreshold=1.00 (GENIUS/MiCA, not tolerant)\n  HALT is EW-driven (not backing-driven)\n  RESTORE is liquidity-driven (T-bill maturity)\n\nOpen Postman Console (Ctrl+Alt+C) before running.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
